title: Setup incentivised options based on KPI's like UMA
body: Adept Camp Agency is all about exploring the latest bootstrapping methods. What UMA is doing here is ground breaking yet quite simple to implement. Lets explore how we can fit this into our strategy to bootstrap liquidity for AC Gov token. And in the process get good implementing these systems so that we can use them on client projects and future venture projects.
author: 0xA42E8966423afAC3F676715d1928CB758aEeCa02
